nodes.text: Yoland Fee was a male Jedi serving the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic during the final years of the Republic Classic era. Master Fee maintained the gardens of the Jedi Temple until the end of Clone Wars between the Galactic Republic and the Confederacy of Independent Systems ended in 19 BBY, and the Supreme Chancellor of the Republic betrayed the Jedi Order and issued Contingency Order 66 to the Grand Army of the Republic, commanding them to execute their Jedi commanders. Led by Dark Lord of the Sith Darth Vader, the 501st Legion stormed the Temple as Operation: Knightfall commenced and Fee was killed in the event.
